# [Visual Studio] NuGet Packages
*.nupkg
# The NuGet offline cache is still used by MSBuild even for SDK-style projects, and its default location is ~/.nuget/packages
# If you create a solution-local packages directory, it will be found by NuGet and should be ignored
**/packages/*
!**/packages/build/

